title: The Great Collection of Punk & New Wave
description:
The Great Collection of Punk & New Wave

500 great songs from the golden age of Punk & New Wave 1976-1984 with a few exceptions. Here are the orginal Punk bands and all the great bands that came in the aftermath of Punk. It was mostley Brittish bands but here are also some american and australian bands.

All songs are in MP3 and few are in 128kbit but most of them 160kbit and more.

I want to make clear that this mine definition of New Wave. I know many also include all the synth music that came out at the same time. I don&#039;t. I have included Pub Rock and the Ska revival that came in the same eara though. Please no complaing about what should be included or what is missing. Just enjoy the songs in this collection. if you miss something I&#039;m sure you can find it elsewhere.

ENJOY!!!
